node.text: Take Action for Our Brighter Future 🏆💖 The 36th Annual Sanrio Character Ranking Contest is here! Tap the link in bio to vote for your favorite characters✨  The winner will be announced later this summer and included in a special capsule collection. Don't forget to share on social by tagging #SanrioCharacterRanking and @sanrio for a chance to be featured!⁠

node.text: From @hellokitty, My Melody, to Keroppi, get ready to discover new residents, styles and items inspired by adorable Sanrio friends! 🍃💞 The #AnimalCrossing Sanrio Collaboration Pack comes to the US on 3/26, exclusively at @target!

node.text:
Our new JapanLA 💚 Hello Kitty & Friends Spirit Jersey featuring Keroppi is here!  Shop now at sanrio.com, @sanriojapanesevillageplaza and japanla.com. Link in our bio✨⁠⁠⁠
⁠⁠
This is an official collaboration between Sanrio, @spiritjerseyoriginals, and @japanla. ⁠⁠⁠⁠
⁠⁠⁠⁠
P.S. Stay tuned for new friends joining the collection each month. Sign up for Sanrio emails to find out when!

node.text:
Like Hello Kitty always says, "You can never have too many friends!" 🌈💕 International Friendship Day is July 30th and we're inviting you to join us in celebrating your Sanrio bestie all week long! ⁠⁠
⁠⁠
From July 25th until August 1st, post a supercute photo of you and your BFF with #SanrioBestie, and follow & tag @sanrio + @retrospekt_ for a chance to win the Hello Kitty and Friends Polaroid camera for you and your bestie! 📸🎀 ⁠⁠
⁠⁠
Sweepstakes ends 8/1. One winner will be chosen and contacted by 8/2 via DM. No purchase necessary. Must be a US resident and 18+ to enter. Link in bio for the official rules. P.S. Shop the limited edition Polaroid at Sanrio.com on 7/30!

Takea PICTURE with your BFF Post it on Instagram with #SANRIOBESTIE 3. Tag & follow @SANRIO @RETROSPEKT_ 2021 SANRIO LTD.'.

node.text: Join Hello Kitty and all her friends as they get ready for the soapbox derby race in the finale episode of Hello Kitty and Friends Supercute Adventures on the #HelloKittyandFriends YouTube channel. Link in bio! 🏁✨

node.text: Better Together 💖 Your favorites have arrived in the newest @stoneyclover x @hellokitty and friends collection! Shop supercute travel accessories and patches online now✨

node.text:

node.text: A dash of cinnamon and a whole lot of pineapple! 🍍🍰 Come bake a Pineapple Cinnamon Dump cake inspired by Hello Kitty and Friends Supercute Adventures. Make the winning recipe from Hello Kitty's Bake Off only on the #HelloKittyandFriends YouTube channel.
